FILE FORMATS

download.db - files the client class is in the process of downloading
<messageDigest>|<fileName>|<fileSize>|<server_IP>|<file_ID>

share.db - files the server class has shared
<file_ID>|<messageDigest>|<size>|<path>
file_ID 0 is always the share index

search.db - files known and what host they're on
<messageDigest>|<fileName>|<fileSize>|<server_IP>|<file_ID>


DEBUGGING LEVELS(set in globals.h)

DEBUG             - enables terse debuggning output.
DEBUG_VERBOSE     - Enables very verbose output. Best to direct this to a file for searching.
UNRELIABLE_CLIENT - 50% chance of "dropping" a received packet.

